title: French Door Leading to Private Patio or Balcony, Recycling, Bike Racks
posting_body: ['Welcome to Bell South Bay in Inglewood, CA!', 'Come home to Bell South Bay, where Life Takes Flight!', 'This luxury community is located just five minutes from the Pacific Ocean and ten minutes away from SOFI Stadium.', 'Situated at the door step of El Segundo Aviation Green Line Metrorail Station and at the intersection of the 405 and 105 Freeways, Bell South Bay’s transit-oriented, “Silicon Beach” location and modern coastal living makes it such a west coast charm.', 'Bell South Bay’s location is desirable to some of the most prominent employers such as SpaceX, Microsoft, Amazon, Boeing, Mattel, Herbalife and Novartis.', 'As part of the Wiseburn School District, residents of Bell South Bay have access to some of the region’s highest-performing schools Da Vinci Innovation Academy, Da Vinci Science and Richard Henry Dana Middle School, all which are located within two miles of the property.', 'Space Saving Stackable In-home Washer and Dryer', 'Two Outdoor Courtyard with Stainless Steel BBQs and Outdoor Fireplace or Fire Table', '24-Hour Fitness Center Featuring Resort Quality Technogym Training Equipment', 'Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances Including Built-in Microwave', 'Controlled Access Community', 'French Door Leading to Private Patio or Balcony', 'Kitchen Island or Breakfast Bar with Pendant Lights', 'Resort-Style Pool with Cabana with Couch, Lounge Chairs and WiFi', 'Bike Racks', 'USB Charging Outlets in Kitchen', 'Co-working Space with USB Charging Outlets, WiFi Access and Two Desktop Workstations', 'Walk-in Closet with Built-in Shelving', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Pricing and Specials subject to change daily and restrictions may apply.', 'Please contact leasing agent for details.']
